title: Neues "Snow Battle" URF auf dem PBE angetestet! (11 Minuten Gameplay)

embed.description: In this video, I tested the brand new URF mode on the PBE, called "SNOW BATTLE ARURF"! I really enjoyed playing and I think that it will be great fun to play when it comes to the live servers! Thank you for watching! Make sure to leave a like/comment if you like the video.
